             was indicted for <rs id="t17790217-28-off158" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17790217-28-off158" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17790217-28-off158" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               forging upon and under a certain paper writing
            </rs> containing as follows:</p>
               <p>Dec. 8, 1778.</p>
               <p>Mess. Jenkinson and Co.</p>
               <p>Bought of 
               <persName id="t17790217-28-person311">
                  John
                   House
               <interp inst="t17790217-28-person311" type="surname" value="House"></interp>
