               </p>


               <p>2 gallons oil - 0 14 0</p>
               <p>A certain receipt and acquittance for 14 s. to tenor following</p>
               <p>December 8, 1778.</p>
               <p>Rec. the contents By 
               <persName id="t17790217-28-person312">
                  John
                   House
               <interp inst="t17790217-28-person312" type="surname" value="House"></interp>
